<item>
            <title>[LU-2777] error handle of lnet_create_locks is wrong</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2777</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;lnet_create_locks() called lnet_fini_locks() to revert allocations on failure, but lnet_fini_locks() can&apos;t free anything allocated in lnet_create_locks().&lt;/p&gt;</description>
