                            <comment id="53137" author="liang" created="Wed, 27 Feb 2013 19:44:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Isaac&apos;s patch for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2884&quot; title=&quot;LNet SMP cleanups&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-2884&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-2884&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; has fixed this issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="52045" author="adilger" created="Fri, 8 Feb 2013 13:16:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Looks like a simple patch to change lnet_fini_locks() to be lnet_destroy_locks() (and change the order of these two functions) would fix this.  Can you please submit a patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
